text: Amy (hope that's how you spell it) was beyond helpful I ordered off the app for delivery and it sent to the wrong location. She was excellent and exceeded at helping me out 5 mins before close. I am very greatful and wish more people were like Amy. Thank you very very very much. Amy you rock truly thankful.

text: Accidentally did a carry out order on the mobile app. Went to pick up with my child who fell asleep on the way to pick it up so I called and explained what happened.  They told me "no problem we'll bring it out to you". I'm so beyond grateful!

text: Pizza was soggy, toppings were skimpy. I ordered double cheese on one pizza and regular order on second pizza and you couldn't tell the difference. Flavored crust were good. I recommend you check your pizza before you walk out the door.
